Keeping Up With The Kardashians Quote Game by NBCUniversal Media, LLC

By enabling, this skill can be accessed on all your available Alexa devices.

By enabling, this skill can be accessed on all your available Alexa devices.

Description Test your Keeping Up with the Kardashians knowledge by guessing who from the fam said what! Alexa will read fabulous quotes from the show and you must correctly guess who said it. Was it Kim, Kourtney, Khloe, Kris or even Scott? Remember to watch the new season of Keeping Up With The Kardashians, every Sunday at 9, 8 central, only on E!
